avdta.gui.editor.visual.rules

Class LinkTypeRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.gui.editor.visual.rules.LinkRule
      • avdta.gui.editor.visual.rules.LinkTypeRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LinkTypeRule
extends LinkRule
    This matches and displays Links of a specific type (e.g. LTM, CTM, etc.). The type codes are specified by EditLink.
    See Also:
